    "longBusinessSummary": "Derayah Financial Company provides brokerage and margin trading services in Saudi Arabia. It operates through Brokerage, Asset Management, Investments, and Investment property segments. The company offers Derayah, an integrated tools for seamless trading, advanced analysis, and real-time market tracking; Global Trade, a platform that invest in stocks, options, and exchange traded funds; Derayah Funds, a collective investment; Derayah Smart, a platform that provides various strategies to assist reaching financial goals; and Mutual Funds Supermarket, a one-stop platform that offers access to a diverse range of mutual funds from leading fund managers; and Derayah Money Market Fund, a fund that provides liquidity due to the short duration of investments. It also provides real estate investments, equity funds, discretionary portfolio management, margin trading, and investment advisory solutions. In addition, the company offers custody, advising, arranging, dealing, managing investments, and operating funds. Derayah Financial Company was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Riyadh, the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.",
